title: Ray Gallen - Celtic Beat (Bodhran Masterclass)
description:
Masterclass: Celtic Beat - Traditional Music from Ireland

A Bodhran Tutorial by Ray Gallen for Intermediate and Accomplished Players

Accompanied by the finest of traditional musicians - Neil Martin, Davy Maguire, John McSherry, Brian McAteer, Breandan O'Hare and Jason O'Rourke
